Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,救雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,救雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么, 这世上谁会\N放走布里格斯少校, 里欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, who in the world\Nlet Major Briggs loose, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了你, 还有谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt couldn't have been you, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不. 没有刑罚了, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. No punishment, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在对我们做出任何伤害\N都为时已晚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's too late for that\Nto do us any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你玩个新游戏吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l have a new game for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 这就是我们赞助给\N双峰小姐节日自助餐的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's our contribution\Nto the Miss Twin Peaks gala buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我满怀希望见到你们中的\N一个能成为那里的赢家.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l fully expect to see one of you\Nup there in the winner's circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:43.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 做梦呢, 诺玛.\N- 别那么肯定.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Dream on, Norma.\N- Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我们一年中\N最重要的日子.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the biggest day of the year\Nfor us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须得有人去\N搞出点名堂来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to have somebody\Nup there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人就配拿这个奖.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who really deserves this title.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是今年.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指劳拉·帕尔默?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Laura Palmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是个能冲冲喜的好日子.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be a good day for healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不只需要1天呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think we need more than a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 诺玛, 他们今晚会\N颁你荣誉奖吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Norma, are they gonna\Nhonor you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝你当选双峰小姐\N20周年纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your 20th anniversary\Nof winning Miss Twin Peaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别提我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的,\N如果你今天还去参选的话, 你会赢的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,\Nif you entered today, you'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你们,\N是想来影响评委的吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you,\Nyou're already working on the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 既然你提到这...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you mentioned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算要投谁一票?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you gonna vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能你要把选票分成两半了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could split your vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨, 爸爸.\N- 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Daddy.\N- Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我今天见过\N最有才气的一张脸.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most intelligent face\Nthat l've seen all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你让其余的人都相形见绌\N让我们看起来都像灵长类了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make the rest of us\Nlook like primates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都拿着什么书啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 《古兰经》,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Koran,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,福音《博伽梵歌》, 《太教法典》,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Bhagavad-Gita, the Talmud,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,《圣经》, 《旧约》和《新约》,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Bible, Old and New Testaments,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,《道德经》.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Tao Te Ching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:06:01.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 我手中拿着的\N这些圣书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, l hold in my hands\Nthose holy books
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,组成了\N人性本善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which constitute\Nthe fundamental framework
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:06.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个哲学体系的\N基本架构.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of humanity's\Nphilosophy of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面\N有我所寻求的答案.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in here\Nare the answers that l seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:16.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算把他们从头到尾\N透彻地读遍, 直到我找出...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l intend to read them\Nfrom cover to cover, until l find...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听我在这儿唠唠叨叨的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me prattling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是杰克的事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Jack, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,才过了一天而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's only been a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:32.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这一周\N不要太痛苦就好.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope it doesn't hurt this much\Nin a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:38.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小蜜糖, 我能给你\N一个永恒的智慧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, may l give you\Na piece of ageless wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是节选自这些册子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,culled from these volumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,时间抚平一切伤口.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time heals all wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那感觉的滋味.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们几乎没有时间\N去彼此了解.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We barely had time\Nto know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:00.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你有过的时光\N都是精华.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the time that you had\Nwas highly concentrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:06.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,精华中的\N精华.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the concentrate\Nthey make concentrate from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我永远不会再见到他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid l'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克是个说话算话的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack is a man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:19.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他说了回来,\N那他就会回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he said that he'd be back,\Nthen he will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:26.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸, 你无法向我保证的,\N但还是谢谢你的祝愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, you can't promise me,\Nbut thanks for wanting to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这儿，其实是向你\N讲一下西雅图一行的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l actually came here\Nto update you on my trip to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对. 开始吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Update away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帕卡家族正通过动用双峰镇的\N储备基金和贷款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Packards are using\NTwin Peaks Savings and Loan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将现金注入\N格斯伍计划.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to funnel cash\Nto the Ghostwood project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但银行保持的\N非常低调.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bank is keeping\Na very low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:49.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎他们不想\N有任何不利影响.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems they don't want\Nany bad publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:56.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊, 负面影响\N正是他们将会得到的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bad publicity\Nis exactly what they're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 去参加双峰小姐\N的选美盛会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, have you given\Nany more thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你考虑的怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Miss Twin Peaks Pageant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打心底里,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可不想做什么\N镇中之花.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't wanna be\Nthe town bathing beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:14.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:20.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但双峰小姐是\N地方的终极论坛.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Twin Peaks\Nis the ultimate local forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:27.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它真的会很鼓舞人心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would truly be inspirational
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个有政治\N触觉的赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have a winner\Nwith a political sensibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将远远胜过\N那些只有化妆策略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that extends\Nbeyond makeup strategies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和秘方樱桃馅饼的参选者, 哼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and recipes for cherry pie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 如你所知,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, as you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,全镇集结，每个参赛者\N都会向全镇的人发表演讲.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each contestant gives a speech\Nto the assembled town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的主题，是我们\N切身相关的环境问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's theme concerns\Nour immediate environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰就是我们要坚定保护的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what we must do to preserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道还有别的方法可以做到的,\N爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know there's another way to do this,\NDaddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 发表演讲吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:09:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, make the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:03.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,协助制止格斯伍.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help stop Ghostwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:07.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们的日子过的更美好.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take us to a better day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他回去休息了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he taken his eyes off it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你来问之前,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before you ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:22.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还派人出去林子里\N彻底搜索布里格斯少校.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we still got people out\Ncombing the woods for Major Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:26.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 鉴于我们和蓝皮书项目\N之间都有联系,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, considering our mutual\Nconnection to Project Blue Book,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信，云顿·厄尔\N已经盯上少校了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe that Windom Earle\Nhas targeted the major.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为了什么?\N- 有意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What for?\N- lnteresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你容许的话,\N我敢响亮的说.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with your permission,\Nl'd like to speak out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}云顿·厄尔早在1965年\N就已经在探索进入{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle has been\Nseeking access to the Black Lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,守夜门的途径了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as far back as 1 965.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个象棋游戏牵涉到的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chess game may involve
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能比我们\N刚开始想像的还要多.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more pieces\Nthan we've begun to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继而,\N值得要去考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then of course,\Nthere's the mysterious circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些围绕乔西的死\N出现的神秘事件.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounding Josie's death\Nto consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事件?\N要怎么去考虑?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about them?\NConsider them how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死的时候-- 我很抱歉\N之前没有提到这个, 哈里,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she died-- l'm sorry\Nl didn't mention this before, Harry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不顾及到\N你的精神状态.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l had to take into account\Nyour mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她当时恐惧的颤抖着.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was trembling with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽可能的说\N像一头发抖的动物.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would go as far as to say\Nquaking like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以大胆猜测说\N是那恐惧杀死了她.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l might venture a guess to say\Nthat it was the fear that killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死的那一刻...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment of her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我看见了鲍勃.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l saw Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿他穿行并\N滑进时间的缝隙.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he had slipped in\Nthrough some crevice in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再反覆思量, 我相信\N他的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon reflection, l believe\Nthere's a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和乔西的恐惧之间\N是有联系的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between his appearance\Nand Josie's fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他被它吸引了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he was attracted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}并以此为食.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding off it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:36.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得鲍勃和守夜门\N之间有关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see a connection\Nbetween Bob and the Black Lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里,\N我觉得他就来自那里.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry,\Nl think it's where he comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这守夜门就是\N你过去提起过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that the Black Lodge\Nis what you have referred to in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那股 "树林里的邪恶."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as ''the evil in these woods.''
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果云顿·厄尔正在\N寻求进入那里,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf Windom Earle is seeking access\Nto that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们势必要以我们的方式\N比他先进入.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is imperative that we find our way in\Nbefore he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那里是一个巨大的能量源,\N哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a source of great power there,\NHarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:58.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,远远超出了我们\N所能理解的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Far beyond our ability\Nto comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:07.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔, 我真该吻吻\N你的小尖头.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dale, l could kiss\Nyour pointy little head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是恐惧.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是恐惧, 里欧. 那就是关键.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's fear, Leo. That's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜爱的情绪状态.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite emotional state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而这期间,\N原来它就一直近在我眼前.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all this time,\Nit's been staring me right in the kisser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:25.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 这真叫人惊讶, 绝配.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, it's marvelous, a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些盘旋在\N我们噩梦边缘的黑夜生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These night creatures that hover\Non the edge of our nightmares
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每当我们放射出恐惧\N它们就会被吸引过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are drawn to us\Nwhen we radiate fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那就是它们的黄油面包.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's their bread and butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个完美的共生.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect symbiosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 大自然,\N设计和外观都完美无瑕.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nature,\Nperfect in design and aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会失望的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not disappoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 鼓足干劲.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, look lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利在望了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道哪里是入口了.\N我们知道闸门几时会出现了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know where the entrance is.\NWe know when the lock appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:56.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在钥匙在我们手中了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we hold the key in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:02.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我要仓促离开了,\N亲爱的人儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my hasty departure,\Ndear one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:07.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,时候已经到了，把我\N心爱的皇后们聚集起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come\Nto gather my beloved queen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,登上我们的\N黑暗蜜月之旅吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and embark\Nupon our dark honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:16.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自从我刺穿了凯若琳的大动脉后\N我一直没有这么兴奋过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't been this excited\Nsince l punctured Caroline's aorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:22.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 我们一定要分享一下\N最后的伤感情调.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, we must share\Na final sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:26.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在葱郁凉亭\N一起相处的这段时光,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During our time together\Nin this verdant bower,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:31.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须承认, 我对你\N产生了一种溺爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l must confess, l've developed\Nsomething of a fondness for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:35.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,传声筒, 伴侣,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounding board, companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:38.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,永远服从和忠诚.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever obedient and faithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总的来说成绩是A，里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An overall A for effort, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:46.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是有点恼火\N你放走了布里格斯少校.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'm still a trifle miffed\Nat your release of Major Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:52.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过, 你将会有足够的时间\N在这事上好好反省, 是不?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, you'll have plenty of time\Nto reflect upon that, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:48.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2, 和3，4步先前.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One and two and three, step four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:52.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再来1，2,--\N让情绪带动着你.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one and two--\NLet the mood carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕你的弱点.\N再多漏点腿.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid of your vulnerability.\NShow me more leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么\N舞蹈啊, 品寇先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a dance\Nis this supposed to be, Mr. Pinkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大自然之舞, 我的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a dance of nature, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这一种庆祝的仪式.\N好了, 女生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a celebration.\NAll right, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:08.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 转身\N向前弯腰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, turn around\Nand bend forward
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,像小树苗一样.\N一颗在风中的小树苗.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a sapling.\NA sapling in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:16.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那样就对了. 再弯一点, 然后停住.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. A little bit more, and hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都弯成这个样子\N到底为了庆祝什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are we celebrating\Nwith us all bending over like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不要质疑你们的\N舞蹈指导所编排的视觉效果!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever question the vision\Nof your choreographer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不过是我玫瑰花上的其中一瓣.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are but a petal on my rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 麻烦大家.\N从一开始数.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please, people.\NOn the count of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:36.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，4.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One and two and three and four.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再来1，2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one and two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:41.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 3，4...\N- 我最爱歌舞大合唱了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- and three and four...\N- l love a chorus line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里能否稍微\N抓紧一点.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf we could just focus here\Nfor a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还得回餐厅去.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've gotta get back to the diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 我们认为双峰小姐\N最典型的品质应该是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what qualities do we think\Nbest exemplify Miss Twin Peaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,美丽和能量.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们是我所喜欢的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way l like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:15:00.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自信, 上帝快帮帮我们吧,\N和善于交际
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poise and, God help us,\Na sophistication
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还要有教养.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:06.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我觉得还有一个主要的因素\N就是独创精神和见解.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l think a major factor\Nshould be originality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 不是应该归为才艺类吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wouldn't that fall under talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有独创精神好啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's always nice when it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就我个人而言,\N体面的外表永远是大事.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally,\Nl've always been big on style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这\N够我忙活了,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think this is enough\Nfor me to work with,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去\N准备好这些评分表,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so l'm gonna go back\Nand work up the scoresheets,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚见吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l'll see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好极了.\N- 再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Terrific.\N- Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再来3，4.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And three and four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 大伙休息一下.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's a break, team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 基巴. 我们休息了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dick. We're on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 拉娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Lana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你介意帮我到储物室\N找点东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind helping me\Nfind something in the storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,储物室?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一个非常重要的\N道具不见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're missing\Na very important prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不清楚.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 打开它不就看到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just flick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:09.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 你到底\N需要找什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what exactly\Ndid you need to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:15.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拉娜?\N- 噢, 是我熄了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lana?\N- Oh, did l do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要找什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:23.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 这样, 我不知道\N那个东西的专业名称是什么, 但...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, l don't know\Nthe exact technical name for it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:30.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么东西--?\N这儿有什么东西看起来像的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anything--?\NDoes anything in here look like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:35.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我想这个就是了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l think this might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:41.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,?, 天啊, 我想你找到它了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by George, l think you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:54.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 现在是下午1:17.\N我刚刚结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, it's 1 :1 7 p.m.\Nl have just concluded
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天代替睡眠的\N第二次冥想.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my second meditation of the day\Nin lieu of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉精神完全恢复过来了\N让我再次感悟到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l feel completely refreshed\Nand struck again by the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有人\N都只不过是生活在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that all of us on this great big\Nplanet Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个伟大行星地球上\N潜在的一粒小分子.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,live at only a fraction\Nof our potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们日以继夜为那幅\N洞穴岩石雕刻忙碌.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are working round the clock\Non the cave petroglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定答案就在\N这幅神秘的版画里.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am certain that the answers lie\Nin this mysterious etching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也确信\N云顿·厄尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am also convinced\Nthat Windom Earle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正在搜寻\N和我们一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is searching for exactly\Nthe same thing as we are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过他的理由却截然相反.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for diametrically opposite reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:22.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,关于那块不洁之地所含能量的假设\N如果我是正确的,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l'm correct in my assumptions\Nabout the power of this unholy place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他捷足先登的话，就只能等上帝打救了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help us if he gets there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 在这个特别的时刻,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, at this particular juncture,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想特别提一下\N安妮·伯本.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like to make specific mention\Nof Annie Blackburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她完全是一个\N原始人类.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a completely original\Nhuman being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她的回答,\N就像孩子般单纯.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her responses,\Nas pure as those of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须诚实, 除了凯若琳\N我还未对一个女人有过这样的感觉.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l must be honest, l haven't felt this way\Nabout a woman since Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,遇见安妮之后\N才让我意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt has taken meeting Annie\Nfor me to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自从凯若琳死后\N我的生活是多么灰暗.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how gray my life has been\Nsince Caroline's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,多么寒冷和孤独.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cold and solitary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然偶尔觉得,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although occasionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,独居\N也不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is something to be said\Nfor solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮·伯本,\N你来得太是时候了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie Blackburn,\Nyou have almost perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的舞指\N可不会这么说.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not\Nwhat our choreographer says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能为你做点什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can l do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 6小时后\N我就要发表演讲了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l need to give a speech\Nin six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我连一个字都还没写,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't written a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不知道\N我要讲什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l don't have any idea\Nwhat l wanna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我紧张的\N掌心直冒汗,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in a complete\Nsweaty-palmed panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要找个人谈谈,\N就是你.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l need to talk to someone,\Nnamely you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的主题是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能做什么\N去拯救我们本地的森林.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you can do\Nto save our local forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想站在那里\N像个神经错乱的芭比娃娃,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just don't wanna stand up there\Nlike some deranged Barbie doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,讲些什么,像\N"确保你的营火熄灭了,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying things like,\N''Make sure your campfires are out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有点像我的脑袋."之类的傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kind of like my brain.''
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你对向公众演讲有恐惧.\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're terrified of public speaking.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那行, 这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我们的森林需要拯救\N因为我们对待它们的方式.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our forests need saving because\Nof the way people regard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是破坏.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果格斯伍的发展\N是以成千上万性命为代价的话,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf the Ghostwood development\Ncost thousands of lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:54.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得它还有\N前进的机会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think it would have\Na chance of going forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然, 树木和人\N不一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, trees aren't the same\Nas people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但它们是有生命的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:04.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的森林是美丽\N而平和的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forest is beautiful\Nand peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,部分已经遭到损坏了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of it's been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试再植,\N但都没法扎根了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've tried to replant,\Nbut nothing's taken root.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:15.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个森林都自己的影子.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every forest has its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能从你的脸上\N看到我半生的历史,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can see half my life's history\Nin your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我不肯定那是否我想要的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l'm not sure that l want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再聊\N树的事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't wanna talk about trees\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道,\N我要和你做爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All l know is,\Nl wanna make love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:13.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和雅吉瓦印第安人的比赛\N他是去年的区冠军.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is me with last year's\Nregional champion from Yakima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:17.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他很可爱, 但有点慢. 下一张.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was cute, but a little slow. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 这是我和\N波咯·法明顿,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this is me\Nwith Brock Farmington,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来自斯波坎市的三A冠军.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,triple-A champion from Spokane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上身很有力,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superior upper-body strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:32.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而四头肌就像桥桩.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and quads like bridge supports.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我用一分零5秒就把他钉到在地了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l pinned him in a minute five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,下一张.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:44.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 这是我\N和我赢得的全部家当.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is me\Nwith all the stuff l won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真好.\N- 恭喜你成功了!.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's nice.\N- Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 现在,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:58.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你们大家都想知道\N为什么我们今天聚集在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l suppose all of you are wondering\Njust why we've gathered here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:04.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出, 我所学到的是，\N当一对夫妇打算离--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, l learned that when a couple\Nis contemplating div--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,分手,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:11.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 有时当有其他人在场\N的情况下，我们会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well, sometimes it's easier\Nto talk about our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,更容易讲出我们的感受.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we're around other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:19.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 纳丁,\N要不，你先开始吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Nadine,\Nmaybe you'd like to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,行.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我猜这一切都得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l guess it all started
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,由我在学校大堂注意到\N迈克的小屁屁开始讲起.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when l noticed Mike's buns\Nin the hall at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:33.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 你现在的感觉怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:38.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 有一点内疚, 我想.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a little guilty, l guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:45.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我意思是, 迈克和我正热乎着呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, Mike and l are hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且双峰小姐今晚就要举行了,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Twin Peaks is tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:51.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是品寇先生觉得\N我很有演艺天赋.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Mr. Pinkle thinks\Nl'm a show-business natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:57.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我是说, 因为我太高兴了,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l mean, because l'm so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心艾德却因此而伤心.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l worry about Ed being sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:06.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德, 你有什么想\N告诉纳丁吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, is there something\Nthat you'd like to tell Nadine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:15.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...诺玛和我\N正计划结婚.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Norma and l\Nplan on getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:22.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 那真是太好了, 小艾艾,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's wonderful, Eddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:29.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为迈克和我\N也正打算结婚呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because Mike and me\Nare getting married too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:27.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那条是去城堡的路?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我等着你呢.\N- 谢谢, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l waited for you.\N- Thanks, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不大说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that he's too talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:50.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他身体上没什么大碍.\N医生抽血化验过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He checks out okay physically.\NDoc ran some blood tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:53.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他被注射了大量的强力安定剂.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been shot full of haloperidol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:55.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:59.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是云顿·厄尔对你做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Windom Earle do this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怪名字.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朱迪·加兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是云顿·厄尔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Windom Earle?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:18.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜，是上帝干的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was God, l suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:21.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰, 他把你带去哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland, where did he take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:22.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是树林吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能讲得具体点?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.77,0:24:28.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:35.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗. 罗马尼亚国王\N不能出席了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.02,0:24:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark. The king of Romania\Nwas unable to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:43.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 这需要点时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.73,0:24:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, this is gonna take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:47.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们还有多少时间?\N- 不大够了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How much time we got?\N- Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.50,0:24:50.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他和我们留在一起.\N或许会冒出些东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him here with us.\NMaybe something will bubble up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.86,0:24:56.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我们这次麻烦大了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.14,0:24:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.04,0:24:58.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果守夜门的入口\N真的存在,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf the door to the Black Lodge\Ndoes exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.13,0:25:01.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它可能会出现在某一个时间点上.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.41,0:25:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it probably exists at a point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.61,0:25:03.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 有目标了, 比如门,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.91,0:25:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, an object, such as a door,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:05.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,通常出现在\N某一个时空点.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.55,0:25:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,normally exists at a point\Nin time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:07.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.45,0:25:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By way of contrast,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.54,0:25:09.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一颗流星通常会存在于\N一个时间点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.85,0:25:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a shooting star normally exists\Nat a point in time
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:11.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,飞越穿过一个空间连续.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over a continuum of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.76,0:25:14.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但从流星的角度去看,\N就是完全不同的体验.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.06,0:25:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But taken from the star's point of view,\Nit's a completely different experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.16,0:25:16.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，你可把我搞糊涂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.46,0:25:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just lost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:19.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不在正确的地方\N正确的时间,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.96,0:25:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf we're not at the right place\Nat exactly the right time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.08,0:25:22.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就找不到入口.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.37,0:25:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't find our way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:24.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.57,0:25:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.35,0:25:27.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,4H俱乐部\N和这一切有关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.64,0:25:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the Four-H Club\Nhave anything to do with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.05,0:25:29.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难说, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.37,0:25:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doubtful, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.54,0:25:37.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是最后一个盒子了.\N看它.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.85,0:25:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be the last box.\NLook at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.20,0:25:39.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也受不了这东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't take any more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.50,0:25:41.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盒中盒.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.79,0:25:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boxes inside boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.81,0:25:44.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里面最好是\N有价值的财富.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.09,0:25:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever is in that\Nbetter be worth a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.51,0:25:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能它根本就不是一个盒子.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.79,0:25:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not a box at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:50.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许它只是\N一块不锈钢.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just a block\Nof stainless steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.52,0:25:53.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 埃卡最后的小恶作剧.\N- 那可真是块好钢.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.80,0:25:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eckhardt's last little joke.\N- lt'd be a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.22,0:25:58.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们召集些\N高智商的人来干这事.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.53,0:25:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's channel\Nsome of that high wit into the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.93,0:26:00.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再来.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.24,0:26:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.36,0:26:03.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不能相信像这样一块小面包屑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.67,0:26:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe a little crumb like that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:07.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然经得起\N千斤顶的虎头钳.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.68,0:26:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can stand up to\Nthis Cram Jack all-duty vise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.37,0:26:12.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,数3下. 1, 2，3!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.68,0:26:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On three. One, two and three!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.04,0:26:17.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 安德鲁.\N都是我不好.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.32,0:26:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Andrew.\NThat was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.53,0:26:26.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢盒!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.20,0:26:35.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.51,0:26:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrew!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.92,0:26:46.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,死盒.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.25,0:26:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.41,0:26:54.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,射得好, 安德鲁.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.72,0:26:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice shooting, Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.84,0:26:57.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.16,0:26:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.98,0:27:00.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一条钥匙!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.30,0:27:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A key!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:07.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有钥匙,\N哪里就有锁.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.30,0:27:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where there's a key,\Nthere's a lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.52,0:27:11.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把它保管好.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.81,0:27:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt should be kept safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.44,0:27:15.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 要一览无余.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:19.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩也互不信任?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two don't trust each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.80,0:27:22.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然信任.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.09,0:27:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:25.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有其兄, 必有其妹.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.12,0:27:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like brother, like sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.42,0:27:29.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.73,0:27:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.95,0:27:33.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,放在蛋糕盘里.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.23,0:27:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the cake saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.91,0:27:36.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一览无余.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.20,0:27:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.87,0:27:42.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么，我们有一条钥匙了.\N- 是的, 我们有.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.20,0:27:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So we have a key.\N- Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:55.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来真美.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.82,0:27:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look truly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.42,0:27:57.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们读一下你的演讲吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.72,0:27:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read us your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.82,0:28:02.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿现在讲一下\N真相.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.09,0:28:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd rather talk about the truth\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.78,0:28:05.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么真相?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.10,0:28:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What truth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.70,0:28:08.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你和本杰明·荷恩\N之间是发生过点事,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.03,0:28:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know something's going on\Nwith you and Benjamin Horne,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.27,0:28:09.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道那是什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.60,0:28:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l wanna know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.84,0:28:12.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜,\N别对你妈妈这样说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.17,0:28:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna,\Ndon't talk to your mother like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.23,0:28:15.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗, 我真的很厌倦\N你们还把我当小孩来说事.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, l'm really tired of you\Ntalking to me like l'm a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.46,0:28:18.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道这到底是怎么回事.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.78,0:28:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.07,0:28:22.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 我理解你的感受.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.38,0:28:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, l understand your feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事情\N你必须要相信.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.38,0:28:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are some things\Nyou just have to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:28.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还年轻\N还不知道所有事情的底线.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.85,0:28:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're young\Nand you don't know all the limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.48,0:28:30.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道谎言的底线.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.75,0:28:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know the limitations of lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.31,0:28:32.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要求我\N要说实话.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.62,0:28:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that you raised me\Nto tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.44,0:28:35.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也对你有同样的期待.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.76,0:28:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l expect the same from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.67,0:28:39.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不打算告诉我\N需要知道的事,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.96,0:28:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you're not gonna tell me\Nwhat l need to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:41.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会从本杰明·荷恩那里找出真相的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.03,0:28:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll find out from Benjamin Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.41,0:28:43.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别.\N- 那就告诉我.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.\N- Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:52.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧, 这是你的选择,\N不是我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.84,0:28:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is your choice,\Nnot mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.21,0:28:55.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.51,0:28:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.39,0:28:58.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.72,0:28:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:16.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,苍天有眼.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.93,0:29:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.73,0:29:19.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 快来看看这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.00,0:29:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.74,0:29:21.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看错\N4H俱乐部的,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.04,0:29:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you mistook\Nfor the Four-H Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.57,0:29:24.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,4和H,\N其实都是占星符号.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.87,0:29:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the four and the H,\Nare actually astrological symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.48,0:29:27.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你意思是, 像行星?\N- 为什么, 是的, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You mean, like planets?\N- Why, yes, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.36,0:29:29.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们代表着木星和土星.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.68,0:29:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stand for Jupiter and Saturn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.27,0:29:31.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其它符号\N也是代表着行星,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the others\Nrepresent planets as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.28,0:29:35.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这幅谜画的特别部分\N涉及到行星运行轨道的确切位置.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.58,0:29:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this particular part of the puzzle\Npertains to a precise planetary position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.33,0:29:38.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 木星和土星要相连了.\N- 那到底是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jupiter and Saturn in conjunction.\N- What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.07,0:29:42.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的, 哈里，在历史上,\N每当木星和土星相连接时,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.36,0:29:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, historically, Harry,\Nwhen Jupiter and Saturn are conjunct,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.25,0:29:44.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能量和命运都会出现\N巨大的转变.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.53,0:29:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are enormous shifts\Nin power and fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.13,0:29:47.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,木星会因其影响\N而膨胀,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter being expansive\Nin its influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.13,0:29:48.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,土星, 则收缩.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.47,0:29:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturn, contractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.57,0:29:52.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,两星相连促成了一种\N强化, 集中的状态.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.90,0:29:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conjunction suggests a state\Nof intensification, concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.75,0:29:55.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这向我显示了\N潜能会因此而出现爆炸性变化,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.07,0:29:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What this indicates to me\Nis the potential for explosive change,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.14,0:29:58.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 善与恶.\N- 那么，下一次相连是几时?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- good and bad.\N- So when's the next conjunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.76,0:30:01.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个, 现在, 让我们看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.05,0:30:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.41,0:30:03.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,根据星历表...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the ephemeris...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.55,0:30:08.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...下一次相连预计\N应该是1月至6月.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.85,0:30:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the next conjunction is due\NJanuary to June.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.08,0:30:11.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的上帝, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.69,0:30:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,守夜门的入口.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.96,0:30:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to the Lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.13,0:30:16.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就会在那时开启.\N就是这幅谜画要告诉我们的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.46,0:30:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it's open.\NThat's what the puzzle is telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.66,0:30:18.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它在告诉我们\N入口打开的时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.96,0:30:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's telling us\Nwhen it's gonna be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.83,0:30:21.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保护皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.13,0:30:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.97,0:30:25.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果它告诉我们时间,\N那么它也一定告诉我们地点.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.30,0:30:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf it's telling us when,\Nthen it must also tell us where.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.06,0:30:30.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧和爱开启大门.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear and love open the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:33.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚刚说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.44,0:30:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.64,0:30:38.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说,\N"恐惧和爱开启大门."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.95,0:30:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said,\N''Fear and love open the doors.''
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.35,0:30:42.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,两扇门, 两个地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.65,0:30:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two doors, two lodges.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.66,0:30:44.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧开启黑色那一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.95,0:30:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear opens one, the black.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:46.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爱, 开启另一个.\N- 那是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.96,0:30:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Love, the other.\N- What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.84,0:30:48.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚.\N它就出现在我脑海里.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.16,0:30:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know exactly.\Nlt just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.97,0:30:52.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皇后怎么--?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.26,0:30:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does the queen--?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.02,0:30:55.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对啦, 皇后.\N- 罗马尼亚的?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Of course, the queen.\N- Of Romania?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.46,0:30:58.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是. 象棋比赛里的最后一只.\N哈里, 跟着我的思路走.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The chess game's final piece.\NHarry, follow my logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.73,0:31:01.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果云顿·厄尔吃掉皇后--\N- 但比赛还是没完，直到他把国王吃掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.00,0:31:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lf Windom Earle takes the queen--\N- Game's not over till he takes the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.04,0:31:04.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,视情况而定. 或许当它开启时，\N他要把皇后带到门外守候着.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.34,0:31:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends. Maybe he takes her\Nto the doorway when it opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.78,0:31:06.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们讲的是哪一个皇后啊?\N- 库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.04,0:31:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Which queen are we talking about?\N- Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.00,0:31:08.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.31,0:31:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:11.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皇后. 皇后.\N皇冠. 皇后.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.01,0:31:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The queen. The queen.\NThe crown. The queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.75,0:31:13.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈里, 皇后.\N- 库珀探员?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.05,0:31:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harry, the queen.\N- Agent Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.93,0:31:15.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 别吵.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.22,0:31:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.36,0:31:18.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 是双峰小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:21.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 圣烟啊, 那就是了.\N- 对. 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.02,0:31:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Holy smokes, that's it.\N- Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.68,0:31:23.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员, 等会儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.99,0:31:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.69,0:31:28.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.97,0:31:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.87,0:31:35.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 原来盆栽装了窃听器.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, the plant's been bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.40,0:31:38.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这盆栽不是乔西送的, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.71,0:31:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bonsai isn't from Josie, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.75,0:31:41.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这盆栽是云顿·厄尔送来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.04,0:31:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bonsai's from Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.93,0:31:43.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他比我们抢先了,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's way ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.84,0:31:46.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从一开始就在\N为他工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we've been working for him\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.37,0:31:48.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 选美比赛几点开始?\N- 马上就要开始了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.69,0:31:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What time does that contest start?\N- Any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.63,0:31:50.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.95,0:31:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.94,0:31:53.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员. 库珀探员!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.22,0:31:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper. Agent Cooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.44,0:33:47.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎, 女士们，先生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.48,0:33:49.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们都有一个愉快的周末.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.81,0:33:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you've had a good weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.97,0:33:52.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位\N来参加双峰小姐选美大赛,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And welcome\Nto the Miss Twin Peaks Pageant,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:56.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些可爱年轻\N又有才的公民们中
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.14,0:33:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which one of these lovely\Nand talented young citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.19,0:34:00.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一位很快就会被加冕为\N双峰小姐呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.48,0:34:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will soon be crowned\NMiss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.68,0:34:04.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 我们的才艺展示环节\N现在正式开始,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.99,0:34:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, commencing\Nour talent section of the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.82,0:34:06.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西·莫兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.09,0:34:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Moran.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.46,0:34:27.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.74,0:34:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.70,0:34:40.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小镇, 伙计.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.02,0:34:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small town, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.43,0:35:00.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了,\N你把全家人都带来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.71,0:35:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what,\Ndid you bring your whole family?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.68,0:35:48.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经动员了大量\N警力进驻全场了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.99,0:35:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pulling in deputies from all over\Nto surround the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.81,0:35:50.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们随时会到.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.13,0:35:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.34,0:35:53.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 重要的是不管谁在比赛中胜出\N都要接受24小时监护,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.63,0:35:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, it is essential whoever wins\Nthis contest receive 24-hour guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.65,0:35:55.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有住宅保安, 我希望这奏效.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,house security, l want the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.56,0:35:56.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等结果一宣布就执行.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as she's announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.13,0:36:00.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的下一位参赛者是\N拉娜·巴丁·妙福,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.47,0:36:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next entry\Nis Lana Budding-Milford,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:03.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她将为大家表演的舞蹈是...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.81,0:36:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who will perform a dance of...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.19,0:36:07.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...神秘异国软体爵士舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...contortionistic jazz exotica.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.76,0:36:10.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拉娜?\N- 库珀探员--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.08,0:36:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lana?\N- Agent Coop--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.21,0:37:15.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看那儿, 我的朋友, 这可是一个真正的艺术家啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.54,0:37:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, my friend, is a real artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.59,0:37:33.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我们森林的方法只有一个,\N就是拒绝袖手旁观，拒绝看着它死去.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.89,0:37:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one way to save a forest,\Nan idea, or anything of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.90,0:37:36.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不但是一种概念\N而且是对一切事物的价值观.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is by refusing to stand by\Nand watch it die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:40.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,自然法则,\N对生命的重要意义
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.70,0:37:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a law of nature,\Nwhich is more fundamental to life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.74,0:37:43.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,远超过了人类所制定的法律.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than the laws of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.00,0:37:46.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当你所锺爱的事物\N陷入危机时,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.31,0:37:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when something you care about\Nis in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.31,0:37:48.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须为拯救它而战
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.61,0:37:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must fight to save it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.58,0:37:50.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就会永远的失去它.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.88,0:37:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or lose it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.63,0:37:53.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.95,0:37:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.16,0:37:58.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 欧蕊·荷恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.46,0:37:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Audrey Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.42,0:38:01.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，为大家穿插一段音乐短剧.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.72,0:38:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now a brief musical interlude.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.08,0:38:04.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.30,0:38:06.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去那儿了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.63,0:38:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.75,0:38:19.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道你和我妈妈\N到底是怎么回事.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.07,0:38:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna know what's going on\Nwith you and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.76,0:38:21.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.08,0:38:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.55,0:38:27.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想最明智的做法就是,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.85,0:38:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think the wisest course would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.25,0:38:30.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,首先, 大家要聚在一起\N然后再去谈论这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.55,0:38:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,first of all, just to get together\Nand talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.34,0:38:31.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不这么认为.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.66,0:38:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.65,0:38:36.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 我觉得现在\N真的不宜在这儿说事.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.96,0:38:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, l really don't think\Nthis is the time or the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.57,0:38:39.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么解释那些老照片,\N在阁楼里荷恩企业的无记名债券,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.89,0:38:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old pictures,\NHorne bearer bonds in the attic,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.49,0:38:41.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那些写给我妈妈的情信.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love letters to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.80,0:38:45.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说真相.\N我想做正事.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.10,0:38:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to tell the truth.\Nl want to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.80,0:38:48.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一张没有父亲名字\N在上面的出生证.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.10,0:38:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A birth certificate\Nwith no father's name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.28,0:38:50.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是搞什么鬼,\N荷恩先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.61,0:38:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here,\NMr. Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.51,0:38:53.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有任何人告诉我真相?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.81,0:38:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't anyone tell me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.91,0:39:02.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.25,0:39:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.31,0:39:08.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈和我...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.62,0:39:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother and l...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.28,0:39:15.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.60,0:39:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.81,0:39:20.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.10,0:39:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.43,0:39:22.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了阐明我的观点,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.77,0:39:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to illustrate my point,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:25.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想引用苏瓜密西族\N西雅图酋长,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.14,0:39:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like to quote these words\Nfrom Chief Seattle,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.30,0:39:27.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的一句名言:
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.64,0:39:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leader of the Suquamish tribe:
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.74,0:39:30.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"你们的死瞬即被遗忘\N并一去不复返.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Your dead are soon forgotten\Nand never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.09,0:39:34.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这曾给予他们生命的美丽世界\N却永不会遗忘我们的死亡.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.42,0:39:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dead never forget the beautiful\Nworld that gave them being.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:36.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们仍热爱它青翠的山谷,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still love its verdant valleys,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.36,0:39:39.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,潺潺低语的川流,\N雄伟庄严的山峦.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.69,0:39:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its murmuring rivers,\Nits majestic mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.67,0:39:42.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当最后一个红种人\N在地球上消失时,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.96,0:39:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the last red man has vanished\Nfrom this earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.63,0:39:45.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些森林和海岸\N仍将怀抱着他们的灵魂."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.93,0:39:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these forests and shores\Nwill still hold their spirits.''
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:48.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，印第安人对地球的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.37,0:39:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the lndians love the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.82,0:39:51.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如一个新生儿的爱\N它是母亲的心跳.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.13,0:39:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a newborn loves\Nits mother's heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.00,0:39:54.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们都失去了\N如此良辰美景?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.34,0:39:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have we all lost touch\Nwith this beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:57.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许拯救森林，要从拯救\N我们内心仅存那点良知开始
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.07,0:39:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe saving a forest starts\Nwith preserving some of the feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:39:59.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每天，它都正在一点一点死去.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.24,0:40:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that die inside us every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.19,0:40:02.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们却极力否认\N那部分属于自己.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.48,0:40:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those parts of ourselves\Nthat we deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.93,0:40:05.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果我们\N不尊重内陆,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.25,0:40:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For if we cannot respect\Nthat interior land,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.07,0:40:09.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不尊重\N我们所走的这片土地.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.35,0:40:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then neither can we respect\Nthe land we walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.37,0:40:12.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，让我们, 在地球上\N轻柔的来去,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let us, in walking gently\Nupon the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.51,0:40:14.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,造福后代.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.82,0:40:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave behind a simple legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.17,0:40:16.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是新时代的斗士,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.49,0:40:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we're new warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.39,0:40:20.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是爱地球并努力拯救它的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.73,0:40:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mystic warriors who love the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.74,0:40:22.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,神秘斗士.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.07,0:40:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.14,0:40:25.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你们.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.47,0:40:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.89,0:40:36.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我们所有的参赛者.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.21,0:40:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all our contestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.46,0:40:40.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,投票现在开始,\N然后我们将宣布我们的冠军.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.75,0:40:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloting will now commence,\Nand we will then announce our winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.43,0:40:46.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都已经忘了\N今天是什么日子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.76,0:40:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you both forgotten\Nwhat day this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.52,0:40:49.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰小姐日?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.86,0:40:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Twin Peaks Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.22,0:40:53.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我那尚未出世的孩子\N迎接父亲的大日子.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.56,0:40:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day\Nmy unborn child receives a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.80,0:40:55.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我要说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.10,0:40:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was right on the tip of my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.93,0:40:58.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.24,0:40:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.41,0:41:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是从个体生物责任感\N去考虑，还是别的,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.70,0:41:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that regardless of which individual\Nis biologically responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.86,0:41:07.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想让安迪做\N我孩子的父亲.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.14,0:41:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l want Andy to be the father\Nof my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.25,0:41:09.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.58,0:41:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.30,0:41:13.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 基巴, 但我必须做最好的，\N为了...他叫什么名字好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.61,0:41:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Dick, but l just have to do\Nwhat's best for little what's-his-name.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.13,0:41:15.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不, 没关系. 一个合理的选择.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.45,0:41:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, not at all. A sound choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.01,0:41:18.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,衷心地祝贺你,\N我最亲爱的安德鲁.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartiest congratulations,\Ndearest Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.79,0:41:23.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 如果你们俩不介意,\N我真的要走了，都等着我投票呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.12,0:41:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you'll both excuse me,\Nl do have a vote to cast myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.63,0:41:28.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是祝小孩的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.93,0:41:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.77,0:41:33.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别用那么沮丧的声调嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.07,0:41:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sound so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.21,0:41:35.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的上帝, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.54,0:41:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:40.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了这个决定\N我太荣幸了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.41,0:41:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so honored\Nyou made this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.44,0:41:45.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证我会做一个好父亲的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.75,0:41:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l promise l'll be a great father.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.93,0:41:49.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.25,0:41:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.89,0:41:53.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.19,0:41:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got to find Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.29,0:41:59.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,男人.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:41:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.74,0:42:06.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,宣布结果的\N时刻到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.07,0:42:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is time\Nto make the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.01,0:42:11.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们新一届双峰小姐大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.31,0:42:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the contest
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.84,0:42:14.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的冠军是...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our new Miss Twin Peaks is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.06,0:42:18.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...安妮·伯本.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.38,0:42:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Annie Blackburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.40,0:42:39.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们，先生们,\N你们的新晋双峰小姐来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.73,0:42:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nyour new Miss Twin Peaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.94,0:42:50.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就是一种侮辱.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.25,0:42:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.99,0:42:54.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这镇上住了\N还不到15分钟.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.32,0:42:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been living in this town\Nabout 1 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.52,0:42:56.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼，脑袋进水了?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.85,0:42:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell got into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.91,0:42:59.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她做了一个精彩的演讲.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.26,0:42:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave a beautiful speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.57,0:43:01.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她言词中带有与生俱来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.89,0:43:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnherent in her message were words
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:04.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是我们中最懦弱的人\N都无不受到感染.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.56,0:43:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the most craven of us\Ncan ill afford to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.13,0:43:24.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.45,0:43:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.41,0:43:37.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,各位, 请,\N请保持冷静.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.72,0:43:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, please,\Nplease stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.23,0:44:01.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.55,0:44:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.02,0:44:04.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.32,0:44:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.19,0:44:32.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静. 各位冷静.\N别惊慌! 这边来.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.51,0:44:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down. Everybody settle down.\NDon't panic! This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.42,0:44:37.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮助你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.75,0:44:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.14,0:44:48.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.46,0:44:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.97,0:44:52.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:55.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.31,0:44:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.50,0:44:57.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈里.\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.81,0:44:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harry.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.98,0:44:59.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他掳走了安妮.\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.28,0:44:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He took Annie.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.55,0:45:01.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他抓了安妮.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.84,0:45:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.29,0:45:04.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西. 他离这儿不会\N超过半英里的. 我们会逮到他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.61,0:45:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard. He won't get half a mile\Nfrom here. We'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.82,0:45:08.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员,\N我一直到处找你呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.15,0:45:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper,\Nl've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.31,0:45:11.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 他们外面肯定\N需要你.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.62,0:45:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, they're gonna need you\Noutside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.79,0:45:13.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这很重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.12,0:45:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.23,0:45:16.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对办公室里的那幅洞穴画,\N我终于想通了.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.56,0:45:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cave painting in the office,\Nl finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.97,0:45:19.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?\N- 我记得之前在某处见过它.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.29,0:45:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- l knew l'd seen it someplace before.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:21.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道它告诉我们要去哪里.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.26,0:45:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know where it's telling us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.76,0:45:23.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它根本不是一幅谜画.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.07,0:45:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not a puzzle at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.72,0:45:25.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是一幅地图.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a map.
